**MtGox Matrix** is a service that provides views of the order book grouped by configurable increments to more easily determine open order sizes.  Additionally the latest trades on the market are displayed.

The configurable bin sizes are: $0.01, $0.005, $0.0025 USD and even tinier increment bin sizes.

